Foocamp Documentation\n					</h1>\n				</header><section class=\"skin-list\"><article id=\"post-191\" class=\"post-191 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">1.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=hosting-requirements\" title=\"Permalink to Hosting Requirements\" rel=\"bookmark\">Hosting Requirements</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>Make sure your hosting supports the following modules.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-191 --><article id=\"post-2652\" class=\"post-2652 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">2.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=foocmap-installation\" title=\"Permalink to Foocamp Theme Installation Instructions\" rel=\"bookmark\">Foocamp Theme Installation Instructions</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>Quick guide how to install the theme and import default content.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2652 --><article id=\"post-2654\" class=\"post-2654 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">3.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=foocamp-homepage\" title=\"Permalink to Foocamp Homepage\" rel=\"bookmark\">Foocamp Homepage</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>The Homepage of the Rounder WordPress theme contains following sections: Slider Countdown Static Text The layout of the homepage is shown in the picture below Slider This theme lets you use powerfull Revolution Slider. Put there any pictures you want and make them different from another Give picture a descriptions and links Each tab of […]</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2654 --><article id=\"post-2657\" class=\"post-2657 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">4.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=foocamp-revolution-slider\" title=\"Permalink to How to Import and Use Revolution Slider\" rel=\"bookmark\">How to Import and Use Revolution Slider</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>Revolution Slider with feautures like responsive, parallax, multilayer adn drag and drop admin.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2657 --><article id=\"post-2658\" class=\"post-2658 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">5.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=countdown-section\" title=\"Permalink to Countdown Section\" rel=\"bookmark\">Countdown Section</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>This section gives you an ability to set up countdown timer. In Countdown setup are available these settings: Image Text Link Custom Width (Leave empty for auto calculation.) You can also set these settings globally that means itâll show on every page. You can also set them different for every page via local settings.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2658 --><article id=\"post-2661\" class=\"post-2661 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">6.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=static-text-section\" title=\"Permalink to Static Text Section\" rel=\"bookmark\">Static Text Section</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>This section gives you an ability to write some text. In Static Text setup are available these settings: Text Text Color You can also set these settings globally that means itâll show on every page. You can also set them different for every page via local settings.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2661 --><article id=\"post-1226\" class=\"post-1226 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">7.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=work-global-local-settings\" title=\"Permalink to Work with Global and Local settings\" rel=\"bookmark\">Work with Global and Local settings</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>In this template you can use two types of settings: Global settings Local settings Global settings Global settings can be found in the General Settings page. All what you have set up in these global settings is set up for all you pages. If you want to have slider, or for example the same appearance […]</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-1226 --><article id=\"post-2663\" class=\"post-2663 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">8.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=focamp-program-feature\" title=\"Permalink to Focamp Program Feature\" rel=\"bookmark\">Focamp Program Feature</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>There are Programs Custom Type where you can add your schedule. Lessons are divided by Locations and Days and ordered by time. If you leave any value empty, it’ll be not shown. There are shortcode [program] available for using Program feature in content. Program custom type consist from individual lessons, whitch have two taxonomies: Location […]</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2663 --><article id=\"post-2666\" class=\"post-2666 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">9.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=foocamp-members-feature\" title=\"Permalink to Foocamp Members Feature\" rel=\"bookmark\">Foocamp Members Feature</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>There are Members Custom Type where you can add members/speakers/people/pets etc. In each member you can set following thigs: There are shortcodes [get_team], [get_teams], [get_teams_category] available for using Members feature in content.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2666 --><article id=\"post-2668\" class=\"post-2668 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">10.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=foocamp-faqs-feature\" title=\"Permalink to Foocamp FAQs Feature\" rel=\"bookmark\">Foocamp FAQs Feature</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>There are FAQs Custom Type where you can add questin-answer pairs. In each faq you can set following thigs: There are shortcodes [get_faq], [get_faqs], [get_faqs_category] available for using FAQs feature in content.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2668 --><article id=\"post-2670\" class=\"post-2670 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">11.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=creating-custom-menus-2\" title=\"Permalink to Creating Custom Menus\" rel=\"bookmark\">Creating Custom Menus</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>How to create main menu and footer menu that will appear on the website</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2670 --><article id=\"post-2892\" class=\"post-2892 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">12.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=how-to-configure-twitter-widget\" title=\"Permalink to How to configure twitter widget\" rel=\"bookmark\">How to configure twitter widget</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>Introduction AIT twitter widget displays chosen number of tweets from particular twitter user. Since twitter released its new API (1.1) there are few steps that need to be done before one can use AIT twitter widget. Because according to new twitter policy every API request needs to be authorized, one must first login to twitter […]</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2892 --><article id=\"post-2672\" class=\"post-2672 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">13.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=setting-up-a-contact-form\" title=\"Permalink to Setting Up a Contact Form\" rel=\"bookmark\">Setting Up a Contact Form</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>For contact form we use a free wodpress plugin calledÂ Contact Form 7. More info about this plugin can be found on the following url:Â http://contactform7.com/ To install this plugin go toÂ Plugins â &gt; Add newÂ and type into search bar âContact Form 7â. Find the plugin and click to âInstall Nowâ. Then clickÂ Activate Plugin.Â A new menu section […]</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2672 --><article id=\"post-2671\" class=\"post-2671 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">14.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=translating-theme-to-other-languages-2\" title=\"Permalink to Translating Theme To Other Languages\" rel=\"bookmark\">Translating Theme To Other Languages</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>You can translate your website to any language. Theme isÂ WPML wordpress pluginÂ compatible. When you have this wordpress plugin then go to Plugins â &gt; Add New â &gt; Upload, upload and activate your WPML package. In WP-Menu should appear WPML button. Click on it and choose languages and default language. At top of Admin should […]</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-2671 --><article id=\"post-291\" class=\"post-291 ait-doc type-ait-doc status-publish hentry no-thumbnail\"><header class=\"entry-header\"><div class=\"title-no-thumbnail\">\n\n			<div class=\"no-thumb-img-description\">\n				<div class=\"date\">\n					<div class=\"day\">15.</div><div class=\"month-year\">STEP</div>\n					</div>\n			</div>\n\n			<h2 class=\"entry-title no-thumbnail\"><a href=\"http://www.ed.be/datadays/wp-admin/admin.php?page=ait-admin&amp;tab=docs&amp;doc=advanced-users-editing-html-files\" title=\"Permalink to Advanced users: Editing HTML files\" rel=\"bookmark\">Advanced users: Editing HTML files</a></h2>\n		</div>\n\n	</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class=\"entry-summary dated-content\">\n		<p>How to edit HTML template and CSS.</p>\n\n	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->\n\n  <!-- /.entry-meta -->\n</article><!-- /#post-291 --></section></div>','no'),(308,'_transient_timeout_doc_9d3faca9fe6acc52d6f4bee4a8f41958','1385301580','no'),(309,'_transient_doc_9d3faca9fe6acc52d6f4bee4a8f41958','<div id=\"ait-theme-doc-single\">\n			<h1>Foocamp Members Feature</h1>\n            \n			<div class=\"ait-theme-doc-update\">\n			 Updated: March 22, 2013, 11:12 pm\n			</div>\n            \n			<div class=\"theme-content-wrapper clear\">\n							\n				<p><a href=\"http://www.ait-themes.com/wp-content/uploads/foocamp-members.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.ait-themes.com/wp-content/uploads/foocamp-members.jpg\" alt=\"foocamp-members\" width=\"763\" height=\"643\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2667\"/></a><br/><a href=\"http://www.ait-themes.com/wp-content/uploads/fcmp-admin-team-member.png\"><img src=\"http://www.ait-themes.com/wp-content/uploads/fcmp-admin-team-member.png\" alt=\"fcmp-admin-team-member\" width=\"1899\" height=\"1419\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2650\"/></a><br/>\nThere are <strong>Members</strong> Custom Type where you can add members/speakers/people/pets etc. In each member you can set following thigs:<br/></p><ol><li><strong>Member Name</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Featured Image</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Specialization</strong></li>\n<li><strong>7 Links with icons</strong></li>\n</ol><ol/><p>There are shortcodes [get_team], [get_teams], [get_teams_category] available for using Members feature in content.<br/></p><ol><li><strong>[get_team]</strong> shortcode renders only one team member. It takes argument id, with id of member and argument icons with possible values yes or no. Argument id is required</li>\n<li><strong>[get_teams]</strong> shortcode renders lastest team members It takes argument number with number of displayed posts and argument icons with possible values yes or no.</li>\n<li><strong>[get_teams_category]</strong> renders teams in specified category. It takes argument argument caetgory with id of category, number with number of displayed posts and argument icons with possible values yes or no. (category argument is required)</li>\n</ol><ol/></div>\n		</div>','no'),(313,'ait-team-category_children','a:1:{i:18;a:3:{i:0;i:19;i:1;i:20;i:2;i:21;}}','yes'),(321,'_site_transient_update_plugins','O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:12:\"last_checked\";i:1385068920;s:7:\"checked\";a:6:{s:19:\"akismet/akismet.php\";s:5:\"2.5.9\";s:36:\"contact-form-7/wp-contact-form-7.php\";s:5:\"3.5.4\";s:9:\"hello.php\";s:3:\"1.6\";s:23:\"revslider/revslider.php\";s:5:\"2.2.3\";s:31:\"tickee-widget/tickee-widget.php\";s:5:\"0.1.1\";s:44:\"wordpress-bootstrap-css/hlt-bootstrapcss.php\";s:7:\"3.0.0-7\";}s:8:\"re