</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Produce a working application </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Draft a business plan to present the results to citizens and entrepreneurs </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Preferably use data from the VKBO and other datasets applied throughout Flanders as a whole. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Develop a plan detailing how you can further market the app, which may result in your nomination for Apps4EU.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The Government of Flanders’ expects that applications should be up and running with a maximum of </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">EUR 20.000.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Criteria for </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">entry include: 1) quality of the application, 2) price for making the application permanently available for at least three years and 3) sustainability of the app. The application may be further marketed by the developer.</span></span></span>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">2. H</span></span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">ack for Good: Lets Fight Poverty!</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">\r\nOver 30 ideas offering solutions to specific poverty related issues were conceived during eight creative miniLABs across Flanders. </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hack For Good</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> wants to turn these ideas into reality. We are asking digital developers, business developers, coders, programmers and hackers to pitch a plan to a panel of financiers on how to implement the ideas that they think are best. </span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The best project will win</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> EUR 10,000 </span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">to boost social innovation. </span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #66696d;\">Criteria for entry include: xxxxx</span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span>Open Europe</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span> | Open World Competition</span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">A</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">re you a creative citizen?</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">If so, </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good News! The </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><i>Citadel on the Move</i></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> project is also sponsoring a competition for amateurs.</span></span></span>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">3. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Citizen Hackathon</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times N